ublic/2023-10/killers-of-the-flower-moon-2023-scorsese-at-table-bts.jpg/960x540-cropped/killers-of-the-flower-moon-2023-scorsese-at-table-bts.jpg","image48x27":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2023-10/killers-of-the-flower-moon-2023-scorsese-at-table-bts.jpg/96x54-cropped/killers-of-the-flower-moon-2023-scorsese-at-table-bts.jpg","imageAltText":"","category":"","author":"","external":false,"standfirst":"At the top of our best films of 2023 poll stands Scorsese’s late masterpiece, an epic story told in intimate terms about the systematic robbing and murder of the Osage of Oklahoma in the 1920s. Here he responds to his win."}],"featuredImage":{"src":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-11/citizen-kane-1941-orson-welles-political-podium.jpg/1300x0/citizen-kane-1941-orson-welles-political-podium.jpg","alt":null,"srcSet":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-11/citizen-kane-1941-orson-welles-political-podium.jpg/510x0/citizen-kane-1941-orson-welles-political-podium.jpg 510w,https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-11/citizen-kane-1941-orson-welles-political-podium.jpg/845x0/citizen-kane-1941-orson-welles-political-podium.jpg 845w,https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-11/citizen-kane-1941-orson-welles-political-podium.jpg/1020x0/citizen-kane-1941-orson-welles-political-podium.jpg 1020w,https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-11/citizen-kane-1941-orson-welles-political-podium.jpg/1300x0/citizen-kane-1941-orson-welles-political-podium.jpg 1300w,https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-11/citizen-kane-1941-orson-welles-political-podium.jpg/2000x0/citizen-kane-1941-orson-welles-political-podium.jpg 2000w,https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/sites/default/files/styles/responsive/public/2022-11/citizen-kane-1941-ors